=\"bb_paragraph\" > Use your arsenal of skills to explore the diverse, dark-fantasy world of Ailur, seeking out written journal pickups, impactful NPC interactions, and unique Kristal Memory items to unravel Kristala's detailed story and lore.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206410/extras/a73499c281dbe1666888c770cc9b633a.poster.avif?t=1771178619\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206410/extras/a73499c281dbe1666888c770cc9b633a.webm?t=1771178619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206410/extras/a73499c281dbe1666888c770cc9b633a.mp4?t=1771178619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Create Your Own Unique Feline Character</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Choose your desired fur pattern/length. Your clan choice determines the type of magic you'll level throughout the game, and your starting class determines your initial weapon, armor, and stat loadouts. Level stats, magic, and feline abilities to fit your desired play style.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206410/extras/4147205a3365269c5b69ab01bde01484.poster.avif?t=1771178619\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206410/extras/4147205a3365269c5b69ab01bde01484.webm?t=1771178619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206410/extras/4147205a3365269c5b69ab01bde01484.mp4?t=1771178619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"